## ğŸ” Authentication Model

| Scope     | Auth Type | Token Variable |
|----------|----------|----------------|
| Platform | JWT      | platform_token |
| Tenant   | JWT      | tenant_token   |

- Platform users manage tenants  
- Tenant users interact with services and bookings  

